For example, a club will earn at least 7.1 million on fixed payments and a maximum of 31.2 million on fixed payments.
On the other hand, Barça have amassed 2.5 million euros for winning the European Super Cup in August.
But there are also variable payments, which are 337.8 million.
This money is distributed according to the proportionate value of each television market.
